<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV32">
<l>mēkaṅka ḷōvurai yīrtiru māṟiru mēṉiyokkum</l>
<l>yōkaṅka ḷuṅkaḷuk kevvāṟu peṟṟī ruyiraḷippāṉ</l>
<l>mākaṅka ḷellān tirintunaṉ ṉīrkaḷ cumantununta</l>
<l>mākaṅka ṇōva varuttun tavamā maruḷpeṟṟatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Clouds? Tell [me], the [good] stars to be equal to Tirumāl’s holy body,</l>
<l>in which way did you obtain them for yourselves? In order to care for the lives,</l>
<l>spreading in all directions, loading your good selves, is it the penance</l>
<l>you suffer, so that your bodies to ache, for obtaining [that] grace?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
